e.tv will add four channels to DStv on 17 May. “This partnership between e.tv and [DStv] gives us an opportunity to deliver top-class entertainment to South African viewers,” said eMedia Investments COO Mark Rosin. The four e.tv channels coming to DStv are: e.tv’s movie channels will be available to Premium, Extra, Compact, Family, and Access subscribers. eExtra and eToonz+ will be available to Premium, Extra, Compact, Family, Access, and EasyView subscribers.